<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Ulm</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass er über die kürzlich erlangten königlichen Privilegien über die Judenschaft zu Nürnberg nicht schriftlich, sondern nur mündlich Auskunft gibt, und bittet um Verständnis.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_511" id="254v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_511_r1l1">Den von Vlme </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_511_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan> habt vmb eın <expan>abſchr<ex>ift</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_511_r1l3">der freyheıt . dıe wır nehſt von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> Jüdıſcheıt <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_511_r1l4"><expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ dem <expan>R<ex>ömiſchen</ex></expan> etc kunıg erlangt ſüllen haben etc das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_511_r1l5">haben wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Nu haben wır ın kürcʒ etlıch <expan>freyh<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_511_r1l6"><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> erlangt / der wır doch nıht <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſchrıft v̈berland <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_511_r1l7">von ſorg vnd <expan>mang<ex>er</ex>ley</expan> ſach <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe darinn ſeın als eẅr <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_511_r1l8">ſelbs auch wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> mag / Vnd <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>freẅntſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> das ın gut </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_511_r1l9">von vns ʒu verſteen / wölt Jr <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>yema<ex>n</ex>ts</expan> der <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> dem Jr des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_511_r1l10">getrawen mugt / ʒu vns <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>ſend<ex>en</ex></expan> . den <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wır vmb <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_511_r1l11"><expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> ſöllıch <expan>freyh<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hören <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> er = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_511_r1l12"><expan>ſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica</expan> dıe <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Matheȷ <expan>app<ex>oſto</ex>lȷ</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_511" id="254v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von Ulme</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        habt umb ein <expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan> der freyheit, die wir nehst
                        von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> jüdischeit <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> dem <expan>r<ex>ömischen</ex></expan> etc.
                        kunig erlangt süllen haben etc., das haben wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu haben wir in kürcz etlich
                                <expan>freyh<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> erlangt, der wir doch niht
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> schrift überland
                                <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> von sorg und
                            <expan>mang<ex>er</ex>ley</expan> sach <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                        die darinn sein, als ewr <expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> selbs auch wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan> mag; und
                            <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr <expan>frewnts<ex>chaft</ex></expan>,
                        das in gut von uns zu versteen. Wölt ir <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>yema<ex>n</ex>ts</expan> der <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>, dem ir des
                        getrawen mugt, zu uns <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>send<ex>en</ex></expan>, den <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir umb
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> söllich <expan>freyh<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hören <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>. Denn wo
                        wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica</expan> die <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Mathei
                                <expan>app<ex>osto</ex>li</expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
